    <h3>
      How to get to the
      trailhead
    </h3>
    <p>
      Access to the Routeburn Track is by road, with the track starting at either
      the Routeburn Shelter or The Divide. The road distance between each end of the
      track is 350 km. Return transport can be pre-arranged to reach either end of the
      track from nearby towns, Queenstown, Te Anau, Glenorchy and Milford
      Sound/Piopiotahi.
    </p>
    
